---
title: Southeast Asian Beef & Veggie Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Peanuts
description: It’s time to master this stir-fry staple in your own kitchen. For the best result, make sure your pan is searing hot before adding the beef. Don’t be afraid to cook the veggies for a few minutes either – you want them to keep a little bite. And finally, top it all off with a sprinkling of crushed peanuts for extra crunch!

*Keep an eye out...Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
